In the terminal window, enter 'git clone' and paste the copied command line, followed by a folder name:
{{ onsCodeHighlight({ "code": 'git clone https://github.com/ONSdigital/ons-website-prototypes.git ons-website-prototypes' }) }}

You can now open this folder in VS Code and start creating your prototypes within `src/prototypes/`.

